short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Power of ChatGPT in Chrome: Seamless integration, engage from toolbar to search results.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
WebWise ChatGPT is a browser extension for easy ChatGPT access without an API. Quick access from the toolbar and navigation bar, with search engine answers. Maintains longer ChatGPT sessions.

- The Best Toolkit for Both ChatGPT Free & Plus Users. 
- WebWise is the ultimate browser extension for accessing ChatGPT! （No API Needed）
- WebWise brings the power of OpenAI's ChatGPT to your browsing experience. Its focus is on reliability and keeping up with its recent changes.



Key  Features
- Access ChatGPT with just one click on the browser toolbar. A pop-up will appear, and you can start a conversation with ChatGPT from there.
- Quickly access ChatGPT from the navigation bar (aka Omnibox) by typing `gpt` and pressing space.
- You can obtain answers from search result pages on popular search engines like Google, Yahoo, Bing and others.
- Run ChatGPT from the context menu.
- Maintains a longer ChatGPT session by periodically pinging it.

We strive to keep up with the fast-paced development of ChatGPT to bring you the best possible experience.


How to use：
- Log in to [https://chat.openai.com](https://chat.openai.com/).
- If you encounter an error, try reopening [https://chat.openai.com](https://chat.openai.com/). The service may be experiencing high demand.
- If you continue to experience issues, please report a bug in the review section of our extension's page.
